-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ABOUT THIS APPLICATION
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This application was built by Veda Moola (IVAO VID 656077).

This is an UNOFFICIAL, COMMUNITY-MADE tool. It is NOT affiliated with,
endorsed by, or officially associated with IVAO (International Virtual
Aviation Organisation) in any way.

This application respects IVAO branding and uses the IVAO logo in accordance
with IVAO brand guidelines. If you identify any branding errors or concerns,
please report them to the application owner via the GitHub issue tracker.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
IVAO DATA
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This application may display IVAO network data (pilot positions, ATC positions,
flight plans) sourced via the IVAO public API. This data:

  - Belongs to IVAO and its members
  - Is used solely for building sector files for simulation on the IVAO network
  - Is never stored, sold, redistributed, or used outside of this application
  - Is fetched in real time and not retained beyond the current session

Use of IVAO data is subject to the IVAO Terms of Service.
If you believe this application misuses IVAO data, please report it
to the application owner via the GitHub issue tracker.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DATA SOURCES
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
This application uses multiple free, publicly available APIs to give you the
best possible outcome when building IVAO sector files. All API usage is legal,
safe, and strictly for flight simulation purposes. No data sourced by this
application is suitable for real-world aviation use.

-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
DISCLAIMER
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
⚠  NOT FOR REAL WORLD USE  ⚠

This software is intended for flight SIMULATION purposes only.
Do not use this software or any data it generates for real-world aviation
navigation, flight planning, air traffic control, or any safety-critical
application. All data sourced by this application may be inaccurate,
incomplete, or out of date.
